SUMMARY:Spring Equinox Sunset Yoga
DESCRIPTION:Join us on the Spring Equinox\, a time of natural balance between day and night\, to discover balance within you! Spring is a season of new beginnings\, for nature and for us! We will create balance in our bodies and minds through an outdoor yoga practice and nature-inspired meditation exercise. Then\, as the sun sets\, we will explore life cycles and tide cycles in action as we take a walk along the Cape May Harbor beach. Please bring a yoga mat or beach towel. \nCOST: Members $20\, Non-members $25 \nIMPORTANT INFORMATION: This program is for adults and children ages 12 & up. Pre-registration is required. Please bring a yoga mat or beach towel. \nWHERE: Nature Center of Cape May (1600 Delaware Ave\, Cape May\, NJ 08204) \nWHEN: Friday\, March 20\, 6 pm-7:30 pm \n\n\nCANCELLATION POLICY: NJ Audubon’s programs require a minimum number of registrants to run. If we cancel\, due to lack of participation\, severe weather\, or unforeseen circumstances\, all participants will be notified as soon as possible and are eligible for a full refund. Participants may cancel without penalty if greater than 48 hours in advance. Sorry\, no refund for cancellations less than 48 hours in advance unless due to health emergencies; however\, registrations can be transferred to another program in the future. \n\n\nREGISTER HERE
URL:https://njaudubon.org/event/spring-equinox-sunset-yoga/
LOCATION:Nature Center of Cape May\, 1600 Delaware Avenue\, Cape May\, NJ\, 08204\, United States
CATEGORIES:Event,Nature Center of Cape May,Yoga
